All Classes

Class Description
Dependency
Base dependency abstraction used to define basic information for dependency retrieval.
DependencyBuilder<T extends Dependency>
Base level implementation of DependencyBuilder.
DependencyEngine
This class is responsible for caching DependencyLoader instances a running them in a sorted order.
DependencyLoader<T extends Dependency>
Abstract implementation of a dependency loader.
DependencyLoadException
Used when there is an error loading a dependency.
DependencyProvider<T extends Dependency>
Base level dependency provider.
InvalidDependencyException
When a dependency isn't able to process this error is thrown.
IsolatedClassLoader
This class handles loading some dependencies that are needed for loading other dependencies, but not need afterwards.
LoaderPriority
This is used to define the order dependency loader's should be executed in.
MavenDependency
Used to declare a maven dependency, it can be defined in two different ways.
MavenDependency.List
Used to store multiple MavenDependency annotations on a single class type.
MavenDependencyInfo
This is the backend class for MavenDependency dependencies.
MavenDependencyLoader
The dependency loader responsible for loading maven dependencies.
MavenDependencyProvider
This class is used to attach dependencies to a MavenDependencyLoader.
MavenDependencyProviderBuilder
Used to build a dependency provider that should be attached to a MavenDependencyLoader then loaded.
MavenRepository
Used to define a maven repo url for the dependencies.
MavenRepository.List
Used to store multiple MavenRepository annotations on a single class type.
MavenRepositoryInfo
Implementation representing MavenRepository.
RelocatableDependency
Used to define dependencies that need to be relocated at runtime.
RelocatableDependencyLoader<T extends RelocatableDependency>
A DependencyLoader that supports relocations.
Relocation
Used to define relocations for any imported MavenDependency dependencies.
Relocation.List
Used to store multiple Relocation annotations on a single class type.
RelocationInfo
Implementation representing Relocation.
Relocator
This class is used for relocating the packages inside of a downloaded jar.
